'''約翰·博齊協會''' ('''JBS''')，是美國一個支持[[反共主義|反共主義]]及[[有限政府|有限政府]]的利益團體。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=MVU6DS6Re8gC&pg=PA576 Principles of the John Birch Society, 1962.] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MVU6DS6Re8gC&pg=PA576 |date=20200807054857 }} "We believe that a Constitutional [[Republic|Republic]], such as our [[Founding_Fathers|Founding Fathers]] gave us, is probably the best of all forms of government"</ref><ref>[http://www.lectlaw.com/files/cur49.htm LectLaw] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lectlaw.com/files/cur49.htm |date=20180617094430 }} "We believe that our system of government, a Constitutional Republic, is the finest yet developed by man."</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.jbs.org/about |title= The JBS Mission |accessdate= 2010-02-18 |publisher= The John Birch Society |url-status= dead |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100223214212/http://www.jbs.org/about |archivedate= 2010-02-23 }}</ref> 他有時也被描述為一個[[激進右翼|激進右翼]]和[[極右翼|極右翼]]組織。<ref name=gomorrah>{{cite book | last = Blumenthal | first = Max | title = Republican Gomorrah : inside the movement that shattered the party | publisher = Nation Books | location = New York, NY | year = 2010 | page = 332 | quote = Skousen's vocal support for the Far-right John Birch Society's claim that communists controlled President Dwight Eisenhower cost him the support of the corporate backers who had paid for his Red-bashing lecture tours. | isbn = 978-1568584171 }}</ref><ref>{{Citation |first=Roger |last=Eatwell |title=Introduction: The new extreme right challenge |work=Western Democracies and The New Extreme Right challenge |publisher=Routledge |year=2004 |page=7 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8Z5wEpDK9d0C&pg=PA7 |isbn=9781134201570 |accessdate=2020-07-08 |archive-date=2017-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323175447/https://books.google.com/books?id=8Z5wEpDK9d0C&pg=PA7 |dead-url=no }}<br />{{Citation |first=Mark |last=Potok |title=The American radical right: The 1990s a